-- Reliance May Enter Health Care, Buy Fortis Stake, Financial Express Says
-- Anil Varma
-- 2010-06-17T01:33:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-17/reliance-to-enter-healthcare-may-look-at-buying-stake-in-fortis-fe-says.html

          
          
             Reliance Industries Ltd. is
considering an entry into the Indian healthcare business and may
be evaluating the purchase of a stake of as much as 26 percent
in Fortis Healthcare Ltd., the Financial Express reported,
without saying where it got the information. A Reliance
Industries spokesperson declined to comment and a Fortis
Healthcare spokesperson denied the report, the newspaper said,
without identifying the people.  
